    <title>攻防世界Crypto新手练习区WriteUp</title>
    <url>/2020/05/04/WAD-Crypto-Noob-WP/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="001-base64"><a href="#001-base64" class="headerlink" title="001 base64"></a>001 base64</h1><p>朴实无华且枯燥的base64（<br>直接解码得到flag</p>
<a id="more"></a>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cyberpeace&#123;Welcome_to_new_World!&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="002-Caesar"><a href="#002-Caesar" class="headerlink" title="002 Caesar"></a>002 Caesar</h1><p>恺撒移位，偏移量为12，解密得到flag</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cyberpeace&#123;you_have_learned_caesar_encryption&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="003-Morse"><a href="#003-Morse" class="headerlink" title="003 Morse"></a>003 Morse</h1><p>将题目附件中1当作 - ，0当作 . ，空格分隔，解码  </p>
<img src="/2020/05/04/WAD-Crypto-Noob-WP/Morse.png" class="">  
<p>得到flag</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cyberpeace&#123;morsecodeissointeresting&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="004-混合编码"><a href="#004-混合编码" class="headerlink" title="004 混合编码"></a>004 混合编码</h1><p>题目打开首先是base64，解码得到</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&amp;#76;&amp;#122;&amp;#69;&amp;#120;&amp;#79;&amp;#83;&amp;#56;&amp;#120;&amp;#77;&amp;#68;&amp;#69;&amp;#118;&amp;#77;&amp;#84;&amp;#65;&amp;#52;&amp;#76;&amp;#122;&amp;#107;&amp;#53;&amp;#76;&amp;#122;&amp;#69;&amp;#120;&amp;#77;&amp;#83;&amp;#56;&amp;#120;&amp;#77;&amp;#68;&amp;#107;&amp;#118;&amp;#77;&amp;#84;&amp;#65;&amp;#120;&amp;#76;&amp;#122;&amp;#69;&amp;#120;&amp;#78;&amp;#105;&amp;#56;&amp;#120;&amp;#77;&amp;#84;&amp;#69;&amp;#118;&amp;#79;&amp;#84;&amp;#99;&amp;#118;&amp;#77;&amp;#84;&amp;#69;&amp;#50;&amp;#76;&amp;#122;&amp;#69;&amp;#120;&amp;#78;&amp;#105;&amp;#56;&amp;#53;&amp;#78;&amp;#121;&amp;#56;&amp;#53;&amp;#79;&amp;#83;&amp;#56;&amp;#120;&amp;#77;&amp;#68;&amp;#99;&amp;#118;&amp;#79;&amp;#84;&amp;#99;&amp;#118;&amp;#77;&amp;#84;&amp;#69;&amp;#119;&amp;#76;&amp;#122;&amp;#69;&amp;#119;&amp;#77;&amp;#67;&amp;#56;&amp;#120;&amp;#77;&amp;#68;&amp;#65;&amp;#118;&amp;#77;&amp;#84;&amp;#65;&amp;#120;&amp;#76;&amp;#122;&amp;#69;&amp;#119;&amp;#77;&amp;#105;&amp;#56;&amp;#120;&amp;#77;&amp;#68;&amp;#69;&amp;#118;&amp;#77;&amp;#84;&amp;#69;&amp;#119;&amp;#76;&amp;#122;&amp;#107;&amp;#53;&amp;#76;&amp;#122;&amp;#69;&amp;#119;&amp;#77;&amp;#83;&amp;#56;&amp;#120;&amp;#77;&amp;#84;&amp;#107;&amp;#118;&amp;#77;&amp;#84;&amp;#69;&amp;#120;&amp;#76;&amp;#122;&amp;#69;&amp;#120;&amp;#78;&amp;#67;&amp;#56;&amp;#120;&amp;#77;&amp;#68;&amp;#103;&amp;#118;&amp;#77;&amp;#84;&amp;#65;&amp;#119;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>看形式是unicode，再解码</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">LzExOS8xMDEvMTA4Lzk5LzExMS8xMDkvMTAxLzExNi8xMTEvOTcvMTE2LzExNi85Ny85OS8xMDcvOTcvMTEwLzEwMC8xMDAvMTAxLzEwMi8xMDEvMTEwLzk5LzEwMS8xMTkvMTExLzExNC8xMDgvMTAw</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>还是base64(老套娃了)，解码得</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#x2F;119&#x2F;101&#x2F;108&#x2F;99&#x2F;111&#x2F;109&#x2F;101&#x2F;116&#x2F;111&#x2F;97&#x2F;116&#x2F;116&#x2F;97&#x2F;99&#x2F;107&#x2F;97&#x2F;110&#x2F;100&#x2F;100&#x2F;101&#x2F;102&#x2F;101&#x2F;110&#x2F;99&#x2F;101&#x2F;119&#x2F;111&#x2F;114&#x2F;108&#x2F;100</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>是ASCII码，解码得flag</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cyberpeace&#123;welcometoattackanddefenceworld&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="005-幂数加密"><a href="#005-幂数加密" class="headerlink" title="005 幂数加密"></a>005 幂数加密</h1><p>先百度一下幂数加密的概念，就是将任意的十进制数表示为2^n或2^n+2^m+……的形式，题目提示flag是八位大写字母，就以密文中的7个0为分隔</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">884210 1220 480 22440 40 1422420 2480 122</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>不难看出8,4,2,1都是2的幂，分别加起来，再对应ASCII码得flag</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cyberpeace&#123;WELLDONE&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="006-Railfence"><a href="#006-Railfence" class="headerlink" title="006 Railfence"></a>006 Railfence</h1><p>W型栅栏密码，用<a href="http://www.atoolbox.net/Tool.php?Id=777.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://www.atoolbox.net/Tool.php?Id=777.com</a>解密，栏数为5，得到flag</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cyberpeace&#123;railfence_cipher_gogogo&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="007-easy-RSA"><a href="#007-easy-RSA" class="headerlink" title="007 easy_RSA"></a>007 easy_RSA</h1><p>已知一次RSA密钥对生成中的p，q，e，求d<br>公式是<code>φ(n) = (p-1) * (q-1)</code>, <code>d * e ≡ 1 mod φ(N)</code><br>直接上脚本求</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> gmpy2</span><br><span class="line">p = gmpy2.mpz(<span class="number">473398607161</span>)</span><br><span class="line">q = gmpy2.mpz(<span class="number">4511491</span>)</span><br><span class="line">e = gmpy2.mpz(<span class="number">17</span>)</span><br><span class="line">phi_n = (p<span class="number">-1</span>)*(q<span class="number">-1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">d = gmpy2.invert(e,phi_n) <span class="comment">#invert（e，phi_n）返回d使得d * e ≡ 1 mod phi_n，如果不存在d，则返回0</span></span><br><span class="line">print(<span class="string">"p=%s,q=%s,e=%s"</span>%(p,q,e))</span><br><span class="line">print(<span class="string">"d is:\n%s"</span>%d)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cyberpeace&#123;125631357777427553&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="008-不仅仅是Morse"><a href="#008-不仅仅是Morse" class="headerlink" title="008 不仅仅是Morse"></a>008 不仅仅是Morse</h1><p>先将题目给的摩斯电码解码得到</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">MAY_BE_HAVE_ANOTHER_DECODEHHHHAAAAABAABBBAABBAAAAAAAABAABABAAAAAAABBABAAABBAAABBAABAAAABABAABAAABBABAAABAAABAABABBAABBBABAAABABABBAAABBABAAABAABAABAAAABBABBAABBAABAABAAABAABAABAABABAABBABAAAABBABAABBA</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>看形式显然是培根密码 把HHHH后面的部分拿去解密得到flag</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cyberpeace&#123;attackanddefenceworldisinteresting&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="009-easychallenge"><a href="#009-easychallenge" class="headerlink" title="009 easychallenge"></a>009 easychallenge</h1><p>（之前新生赛有这题）<br>附件为pyc文件，需要反编译出py文件，之前第一次做用的是EasyPythonDecompiler，后来百度发现大家都用uncompyle6  </p>
<img src="/2020/05/04/WAD-Crypto-Noob-WP/2.png" class="">  
<img src="/2020/05/04/WAD-Crypto-Noob-WP/3.png" class="">  
<p>得到的代码就是上面这样，按着加密代码写一遍逆过程解密就可以得到flag</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> base64</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">decode1</span><span class="params">(ans)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">    s = <span class="string">''</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> ans:</span><br><span class="line">        x = ord(i) - <span class="number">25</span></span><br><span class="line">        x = x ^ <span class="number">36</span></span><br><span class="line">        s += chr(x)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> s</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">decode2</span><span class="params">(ans)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">    s = <span class="string">''</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> ans:</span><br><span class="line">        x = ord(i) ^ <span class="number">36</span></span><br><span class="line">        x = x - <span class="number">36</span></span><br><span class="line">        s += chr(x)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> s</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">decode3</span><span class="params">(ans)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> base64.b32decode(ans)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">flag = <span class="string">''</span></span><br><span class="line">final = <span class="string">'UC7KOWVXWVNKNIC2XCXKHKK2W5NLBKNOUOSK3LNNVWW3E==='</span></span><br><span class="line">t = decode3(final)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> t:</span><br><span class="line">    flag += chr(i) <span class="comment">#这里t的类型是bytes，直接丢进decode2里会报错，所以先转成str</span></span><br><span class="line">flag = decode1(decode2(flag)) </span><br><span class="line">print(flag)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#flag：cyberpeace&#123;interestinghhhhh&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="010-Normal-RSA"><a href="#010-Normal-RSA" class="headerlink" title="010 Normal_RSA"></a>010 Normal_RSA</h1><p>题目给了pem格式的公钥文件和enc格式的被加密的flag，可以用RsaCtfTool直接解密<br>项目地址：<a href="https://github.com/Ganapati/RsaCtfTool" target="_blank" rel="noopener">RsaCtfTool</a>  </p>
<img src="/2020/05/04/WAD-Crypto-Noob-WP/4.png" class="">  
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">PCTF&#123;256b_i5_m3dium&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="011-转轮机加密"><a href="#011-转轮机加密" class="headerlink" title="011 转轮机加密"></a>011 转轮机加密</h1><p>小学时读的可怕的科学系列里的《密码全攻略》里提到过这种加密方式，印象深刻  </p>
<img src="/2020/05/04/WAD-Crypto-Noob-WP/5.png" class="">  
<p>这道题中，将横行按密钥顺序排列对齐，每一横行看作一个转盘，将密文中每个字母按顺序转到每一行的第一列，然后一列列看过去，可读的那列就是flag<br>也可以用python写脚本做，但这题不是明显直接上手操作更快吗（</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">flag: fireinthehole(这题不需要cyberpeace&#123;&#125;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="012-easy-ECC"><a href="#012-easy-ECC" class="headerlink" title="012 easy ECC"></a>012 easy ECC</h1><p>ECC的相关知识来自<a href="https://www.freebuf.com/articles/database/155912.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">椭圆曲线算法（ECC）学习（一）</a>以及<a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/e41bc1eb1d81" target="_blank" rel="noopener">椭圆曲线加密算法</a>  </p>
<p>这道题给出了椭圆曲线Ep(a, b)和基点G(x, y)以及私钥k，要求计算公钥K = kG  </p>
<p>有限域GF(p)上的椭圆曲线y² = x³ + ax + b，若P(Xp, Yp), Q(Xq, Yq)，且P≠-Q，则R(Xr,Yr) = P+Q 由如下规则确定：  </p>
<p>Xr = (λ² - Xp - Xq) mod p<br>Yr = (λ (Xp - Xr) - Yp) mod p<br>其中,<br>λ = (Yq - Yp) / (Xq - Xp) mod p（若P ≠ Q）<br>λ = (3Xp² + a) / 2Yp mod p（若P = Q）  </p>
<p>因此，以有限域GF(23)上的椭圆曲线y² ≡ x³ + x + 1 (mod 23)为例，假设以(0,1)为G点，计算2G、3G、4G…xG等等，方法如下：</p>
<p>计算2G：<br>λ = (3x0² + 1)/2x1 mod 23 = (1/2) mod 23 = 12<br>Xr = (12² - 0 - 0) mod 23 = 6<br>Yr = (12(0 - 6) - 1) mod 23 = 19<br>即2G为点(6,19)</p>
<p>计算3G：<br>3G = G + 2G，即(0,1) + (6,19)<br>λ = (19 - 1)/(6 - 0) mod 23 = 3<br>Xr = (3² - 0 - 6) mod 23 = 3<br>Yr = (3(0 - 3) - 1) mod 23 = 13<br>即3G为点(3, 13)<br>同理可计算4G，5G，… ，kG  </p>
<p>了解了计算公式和基本原理后，直接上脚本<br>（脚本来自<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/cccchhhh6819/article/details/100660139" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://blog.csdn.net/cccchhhh6819/article/details/100660139</a>）</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> gmpy2 <span class="keyword">import</span> invert</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">ECCnegative</span><span class="params">(x, y, p)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> x, p-y</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">ECCadd</span><span class="params">(x1, y1, x2, y2, p, a)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(x1==x2):</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span>((y1+y2)%p==<span class="number">0</span>):</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">-1</span>, <span class="number">-1</span> <span class="comment"># infinity return</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">elif</span>(y1!=y2):</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">print</span> (<span class="string">"Input Error, Please check the input!"</span>)</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">-2</span>, <span class="number">-2</span> <span class="comment"># error input return</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span>:</span><br><span class="line">            k = ((<span class="number">3</span> * x1 * x1 + a) * invert(<span class="number">2</span> * y1, p)) % p</span><br><span class="line">            x3 = (k * k - x1 - x2) % p</span><br><span class="line">            y3 = (k * (x1 - x3) - y1) % p</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> int(x3), int(y3)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">else</span>:</span><br><span class="line">        k = ((y2 - y1) * invert(x2 - x1, p))%p</span><br><span class="line">        x3 = (k * k - x1 - x2) % p</span><br><span class="line">        y3 = (k * (x1 - x3) - y1) % p</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> int(x3), int(y3)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">ECCmul</span><span class="params">(k, x, y, p, a)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">    tempx, tempy = <span class="number">-1</span>, <span class="number">-1</span></span><br><span class="line">    nowx, nowy = x, y</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span>(k != <span class="number">0</span>):</span><br><span class="line">        mark = k &amp; <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">        k = k &gt;&gt; <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span>(mark == <span class="number">1</span>):</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span>(tempx == <span class="number">-1</span>):</span><br><span class="line">                tempx, tempy = nowx, nowy</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">else</span>:</span><br><span class="line">                tempx, tempy = ECCadd(tempx, tempy, nowx, nowy, p, a)</span><br><span class="line">        nowx, nowy = ECCadd(nowx, nowy, nowx, nowy, p, a)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> tempx, tempy</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">p = <span class="number">15424654874903</span></span><br><span class="line">a = <span class="number">16546484</span></span><br><span class="line">b = <span class="number">4548674875</span></span><br><span class="line">x = <span class="number">6478678675</span></span><br><span class="line">y = <span class="number">5636379357093</span></span><br><span class="line">k = <span class="number">546768</span></span><br><span class="line">(ax, ay) = ECCmul(k, x, y, p, a)</span><br><span class="line">print(ax + ay)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cyberpeace&#123;19477226185390&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h1 id="The-End"><a href="#The-End" class="headerlink" title="The End"></a>The End</h1><p>完结撒花！  </p>
<img src="/2020/05/04/WAD-Crypto-Noob-WP/end.jpg" class="">

]]></content>
